metadata.recording_metadata_summary: This recording is from a middle-school participating in the PLUS tutoring program. This school is called Urban Pathways. Students in this school use Chromebooks to access Zoom and generally use the math software Khan. The teacher in the classroom is named Moloney, although other teachers may be present. The tutor assigned to this classroom is named Alicia Chen, although other tutors may be present.
